data.description: Location, Location, Location! SPACIOUS 3 bedroom home in the North Firs Community of Puyallup. Located right off Meridian, this rare gem is in a community where YOU OWN THE LAND! No park rent! Not a 55+ Community either! Lots of upgrades by the current owners as well... new cedar fence, new gutters, new bath insert, new flooring through main living areas, and more! Open and functional floorplan with 2 separate living/great rooms. Primary bedroom is at the opposite end of the house from the other bedrooms as well. Long carport easily fits 2 vehicles. Store your tools and hobbies in the attached shop. Brand new "tough shed" in the backyard stays too! All this for under $400K, with a $10,000 buyers bonus!! Ask your agent for details!
